# The Hono API source (server/src) is bundled into the Next.js build via the
# /api catch-all route, so it MUST be uploaded. The backend dir is named
# `server/` (NOT `api/`) on purpose: Vercel's zero-config convention turns a
# root-level `api/**/*.ts` into one Serverless Function per file, which blows
# the Hobby 12-function cap. Only exclude what the build does not need.
supabase/
docs/
server/tests/
server/dist/
server/node_modules/
